  "message": "chore: add .env to gitignore and add MCP config files for codex, cursor, and gemini\n\nAdd .env to .gitignore to prevent accidental commit of environment secrets.\n\nAdd MCP (Model Context Protocol) server configuration files for three\nagent frontends \u2014 codex.mcp.json, cursor.mcp.json, and gemini.mcp.json \u2014\npointing at the local mcp-agent-mail HTTP endpoint. These enable AI\ncoding agents to communicate via the shared mailbox infrastructure.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
